        "id": "HigherSpiritGroundPlus",
        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Oppressive Ground",
          "description": "If this unit would be defeated, it instead survives with 1 HP and then cannot be defeated until its next turn. This effect can be triggered once each time this unit enters the battlefield. Whenever this unit uses Spirit Crash, this Hold Ground+ effect is reset so it can trigger again.\n\nSteals 1 Spirit from the enemy team whenever this unit deals damage with an attack. Attacks that target multiple enemies will trigger this once for each enemy they damage.\n\nThis unit has 65% damage reduction from attacks unless this unit has defeated an enemy while on the battlefield."
        }
      },
      "BoomAndBustQuickenedLethal": {
        "id": "BoomAndBustQuickenedLethal",
        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Berserker's Requiem",
          "description": "Every time an ally starts their turn with 10 Spirit, or an enemy starts theirs with 0 Spirit, this unit enters Berserker Form at the end of that turn.\n\nWhile in Berserker Form, this unit's active skill TU costs are reduced by 40%, and this unit's attacks will ignore any effects of non-boss enemies that would prevent the target from being defeated. Berserker Form ends when this unit defeats an enemy with an attack, and can then be triggered again.\n\nWhenever this unit is defeated by an enemy, steals Spirit from the enemy team until either ally Spirit reaches 10, or enemy Spirit reaches 0."
        }
      },
